title: Invitation to launch event on Thursday 22 October 2015 (Hertfordshire County Council)
text: ( Source : Hertfordshire County Council ) You are invited to attend the launch of a new Carers' Strategy for Hertfordshire Come and talk to key spokespeople from Hertfordshire County Council, Hertfordshire Clinical Commissioning Groups (CCGs)
